"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"### Get account\\n\\nQuery for [an account](https://github.com/cosmos/cosmos-sdk/tree/main/x/auth#account-1) by it's address.\\n\\n#### Method Declaration\\n\\n:::code-group\\n\\n```python [Python]\\nasync def get_account(self, address: str) -> BaseAccount\\n```\\n\\n```rust [Rust]\\npub async fn get_account(&mut self, address: &Address) -> Result<BaseAccount, Error>\\n```\\n\\n```typescript [TypeScript]\\n```\\n\\n```url [API]\\n```\\n\\n:::\\n\\n#### Parameters\\n\\n\\n#### Response\\n\\nExamples: [Python] | [TypeScript] | [Rust]\\n\\n[Python]:https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-py-v2/examples/basic_adder.py#L159\\n[Rust]: https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-rs/client/examples/wallet.rs#L89\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/noble-client/get_account#get-account\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Query for <a href=\\\"https://github.com/cosmos/cosmos-sdk/tree/main/x/auth#account-1\\\">an account</a> by it&#x27;s address.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/noble-client/get_account.mdx#get-account\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nQuery for an account by it&#x27;s address.\\n\",\"title\":\"Get account\",\"titles\":[null,null]},{\"href\":\"/noble-client/get_account#method-declaration\",\"html\":\"\\n<div class=\\\"code-group\\\"><div data-title=\\\"Python\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Python\\\" data-lang=\\\"python\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">async</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> def</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\"> get_account</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(self, address: </span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">str</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">) -&gt; BaseAccount</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"Rust\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Rust\\\" data-lang=\\\"rust\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">pub</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> async</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> fn</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\"> get_account</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&amp;mut</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> self</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">, address</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">:</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> &amp;</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">Address</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">-&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> Result</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">BaseAccount</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">, </span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">Error</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"TypeScript\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"TypeScript\\\" data-lang=\\\"typescript\\\"><co